# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

We release patches for security vulnerabilities. Which versions are supported receiving security updates?

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 1.x     | :white_check_mark: |
| < 1.0   | :x:                |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

Please report security vulnerabilities by email to **security@gitdigital.org**.

You should receive a response within 48 hours. If the issue is confirmed, we will release a patch as soon as possible, typically within a few days.

For critical issues, you can also open a draft security advisory on GitHub:  
[Create a new security advisory](https://github.com/Gitdigital-products/Grant-Program-Management-repo/security/advisories/new)

Please do **not** open public issues for security vulnerabilities.
```

